OL,3,CDeborah James's family urge political
OL,4,Cparties to commit to long-term cancer
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FDame Deborah James' family is urging
OL,8,Fpoliticians to help give people
OL,9,Faffected by cancer more time with the
OL,10,Fpeople they love, as ITV News Reporter
OL,11,FChloe Keedy explains
OL,13,FThe family of Dame Deborah James have
OL,14,Furged all UK political parties to
OL,15,Fcommit to a long-term cancer strategy
OL,16,F"to give more people affected by
OL,17,Fcancer more time with the people they
OL,18,Flove".
