OL,3,CDeborah James's family urge political
OL,4,Cparties to commit to long-term cancer
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FDame Deborah died in June 2022 at the
OL,8,Fage of 40, five years after she was
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with bowel cancer.
OL,11,FThe journalist used her diagnosis to
OL,12,Fraise awareness of the disease and set
OL,13,Fup the Bowelbabe Fund for Cancer
OL,14,FResearch UK, which has raised more
OL,15,Fthan #12 million.
