OL,3,CDeborah James's family urge political
OL,4,Cparties to commit to long-term cancer
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FIn a letter published in the Sun
OL,8,Fnewspaper, Dame Deborah's husband
OL,9,FSebastien Bowen, her parents Alistair
OL,10,Fand Heather James and her siblings Ben
OL,11,FJames and Sarah Wieczorek, said they
OL,12,Fare joining Cancer Research UK in
OL,13,Ftheir Longer, Better Lives manifesto.
OL,15,FThe manifesto calls for the Government
OL,16,Fto publish a long-term cancer strategy
OL,17,Fwithin one year of the general
OL,18,Felection, to "drive earlier diagnosis
OL,19,Fand reduce inequalities in access to
OL,20,Ftreatment and care".
