OL,3,CDeborah James's family urge political
OL,4,Cparties to commit to long-term cancer
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,F"That is why we are calling on all
OL,8,Fpolitical parties to make the upcoming
OL,9,Fgeneral election a landmark moment by
OL,10,Fcommitting to a long-term cancer
OL,11,Fstrategy for England, helping to give
OL,12,Fmore people affected by cancer more
OL,13,Ftime with the people they love," the
OL,14,Fletter said.
